Workshop on Demand System
-------------------------

Loosely based on Doodle and Pleft web applications.
Works with Google Apps for Education.

1. Set up an account in your Google Apps organization. The personal 
calendar for this account will hold the workshop events.

2. Configure app_config.yml based on app_config.yml.sample file.

3. Create database.

4. Profit!

